Android RoadMap
----------------

1. Pick a Language

	   - Kotlin
	   - Java

2. The Fundamentals

	   - Development IDE
	   - Basics of Kotlin
	   - Basics of OOP
	   - DataStructures and Algorithms
	   - What is and how to use Gradle?
	   - Create a basic Hello World App

3. Version Control Systems

       - Git
	   - GitHub
	   - BitBucket
	   - GitLab

4. App Components

       - Activity
	        - Activity Lifecycle
			- State Changes
			- Tasks and Backstack
	   - Services
	   - Content Provider
	   - Broadcast Receiver
	   - Intent
	        - Implicit Intents
			- Explicit Intents
			- Intent Filters

5. Interface and Navigation

		- Layouts
		    - Frame
			- Linear
			- Relative
			- Constraint
			- RecycleView
		- Elements
			- TextView
			- Fragments
			- EditText
			- Dialogs
			- Buttons
			- Toast
			- ImageView
			- Bottom Sheet
			- ListView
			- Drawer
			- Tabs
			- Animations
		- Jetpack Compose
            - App Shortcuts
			- Navigation Components

6. Architecture and Design Patterns

        - MVC
		- MVP
		- MVVM
		- MVI
		- Repository Pattern
		- Builder Pattern
		- Observer Pattern
		   - LiveData
		   - RxKotlin
		   - RxJava
		   - Flow
		- Dependency Injection
		    - Dagger
			- Hilt
			- Koin
			- Kodein
		- Factory Pattern

7. Storage

	   - Shared Preferences
	   - DataStore
	   - Room Database
	   - File System

8. Network

	   - Retrofit
	   - OkHttp
	   - Apollo-Android

9. Asynchronism

       - Coroutines
       - Threads
       - RxJava
       - RxKotlin
       - WorkManager

10. Common Services

       - Firebase
	      - FireStore
		  - Cloud Messaging
		  - Remote Config
		  - Crashlytics
		  - Authentication
	   - Google AdMob
       - Google Play Services
       - Google Maps

11. Linting

         - Ktlint
		 - Detekt

12. Debugging

         - Timber
		 - Timber
		 - Chucker
		 - Jetpack Benchmark

13. Testing

		  - JUnit
		  - Espresso

14. Distribution

          - Google Playstore
          - Firebase Distribution
          - Signed APK


Android Studio Shortcutkeys
